The paper deals with video retrieval using natural language queries, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of pretrained semantic embeddings, which falls under the category of multimedia (MM) and information retrieval (IR). Finally, the paper proposes a collaborative experts model, which involves machine learning (LG) techniques.
